&lt;p&gt;SimpleACLTest..testServerPublishInvalidQueueSuccess&lt;br/&gt;
junit.framework.AssertionFailedError: Incorrect exception expected:&amp;lt;class javax.jms.IllegalStateException&amp;gt; but was:&amp;lt;class javax.jms.JMSException&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
